  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="Aink300-kilavi">talaimakaṉ tāṉē varaivu vēṇṭiviṭac cuṟṟattār koṭai nērntamai talaimakaṭkut tōḻi colliyatu. </p>
        <p xml:lang="en"> 
          What the confidante told the heroine: that, as the hero himself desired marriage, [her] relatives agreed to give [her away].        
        </p>
      </div>
      <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink300">
<l>koṭicci kūntal pōlat tōkai</l>
<l>yañciṟai virikkum peruṅkal veṟpaṉ</l>
<l>vantaṉa ṉetirntaṉar koṭaiyē</l>
<l>yantīṅ kiḷavi polikaniṉ ciṟappē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
        <l>The man from the mountain with big stones,</l>
        <l>where a peacock spreads its beautiful plumes</l>
        <l>like the hair of a creeper woman,</l>
        <l>has come. They [your family] have agreed to give [you].</l>
        <l rend="space">O one of lovely, sweet words—may your eminence flourish!</l>
        
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
